title: LOOK NO FURTHER! ONE BED AVAILABLE
posting_body: ['LISTING ID 6432407', 'This apartment located in a rental community in Fort Lauderdale features one, two and three bedroom floor plans,', 'a fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, a dishwasher, porcelain tile flooring, a living room and a dining room.', 'Enjoy the comforts of elevators, keyless entry, 9 foot ceilings, central A/C, in-unit laundry and off-street garage parking.', 'The community offers a clubhouse with a business center,', 'a resident lounge, outdoor kitchen with grill, dual spas with sauna, shower and lockers, two on site pet spas, five fitness studios, outdoor yoga, outdoor putting green,', 'two bike rooms, outdoor gaming area, indoor movie room, zen garden with hammocks, sports lounge with poker table and pool table, rentable private offices, co-working areas, pool with a sundeck and a fitness center.', 'This community is also deleaded and pet friendly.', 'Located within a five minute drive to the US-1.', 'LISTING ID 6432407', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
